{"word":"ὄχησις","slug":"ὄχησις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὄχησις</b></el> <el>(ὄχησις, εως,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὀχέω'><el>ὀχέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a bearing, carrying</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(from <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>) <i>a being carried</i>, <el>ἵππων ὀχήσεις</el> <i>riding</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}